              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Radiative capture cross section was determined as:",
                " (8/3)*PI*SIG(90deg), which is suitable for the case of",
                "angular distribution corresponding to the function",
                " SIN**2 .This dependence was indicated by measured",
                "relationship of gamma-ray intensities at 90 and 45 deg.",
                "angles equal to 1.8+-0.20."
              ]
